  • Uses of EventInfo in backEnd

    Methods in backEnd that return EventInfo 
    Modifier and Type Method Description
    EventInfo RescueSailors.findSailors​(Ship ship)
    Player finds some sailors and rescues them
    In return, those sailors reward the player with coins
    EventInfo Pirates.pirateBattle​(Ship shipName)
    Player meets pirates and needs to play a dice game to battle with them
    EventInfo Player.setSail​(Route route, Island destination)
    Player takes a route to travel to an island with probability of random events
    EventInfo Weather.storm​(Ship ship)
    A storm hits the ship when the player is sailing
    This will add some damage to the ship and requires repair before sailing again
